@page "/codeofconduct"
@inject HttpClient Http

<PageTitle>.NET Community: Code of Conduct</PageTitle>

<MudText Typo=Typo.h4 Class="pb-4">.NET foundation: Code of Conduct</MudText>
<MudText Typo=Typo.body1 Class="pb-4">
    As a guest (or host) of any of the .NET streams (either live or pre-recorded), your participation is considered a
    content contribution. We strive to foster an open and inclusive environment for all. To that end, we adhere to
    the <i>.NET foundation's Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct</i>.
    <MudSpacer />
</MudText>
<MudLink Href="https://dotnetfoundation.org/about/code-of-conduct" Target="_blank">
    <MudImage Src="dotnet-foundation-logo.svg" Alt=".NET foundation" />
</MudLink>
<MudDivider Class="my-4" />
<MudText Typo=Typo.body1 Class="pb-4">
    In addition to adhering to the .NET foundation's Contributor Covenant Code of Conduct, we also 
    follow the community guidelines of the platforms where we stream.
</MudText>

<MudText Typo=Typo.h5 Class="pb-4">Twitch.TV: Community Guidelines</MudText>
<MudFab StartIcon=@Icons.Material.Filled.Link Size=Size.Large
    IconSize=Size.Large IconColor=Color.Primary Target="_blank"
    Href="https://safety.twitch.tv/s/article/Community-Guidelines" />

<MudDivider Class="my-4" />

<MudText Typo=Typo.h5 Class="pb-4">YouTube: Community Guidelines</MudText>
<MudFab StartIcon=@Icons.Custom.Brands.YouTube Size=Size.Large 
    IconSize=Size.Large Color=Color.Error Target="_blank"
    Href="https://www.youtube.com/howyoutubeworks/policies/community-guidelines" />